<div class="col-12 col-md-8 flex --direction-col --justify-content-center article-contributor-main">
<div class="article-contributor__meta-container">
<h1 class="article-contributor-section_title">James Pogue</h1>
<p class="article-contributor-section_content">James Pogue is the author of <em>Chosen Country: A Rebellion in the West</em>, and is a contributing editor at <em>Harper’s Magazine</em>. He is writing a book about rural California. The Pulitzer Center helped fund his reporting for ‘Wagner in Africa’.</p>
<a class="article-contributor-section_link" href="https://granta.com/james-pogue">More about the author →</a>
